            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>(tomb of) Alliena Dorothea</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>For the name Alliena/us (attested several times at Lipara), note <ref target="http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/person/2324">A. Allienus</ref>, legatus of Q. Cicero in Asia in 60, was governor of Sicily 48-46 BC. <ref target="http://www.lgpn.ox.ac.uk/id/V3a-38315">Dorothea</ref> is not otherwise attested in Sicily.</p>
            </div>
